               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img src=\"images/Mapswire/mapswire-continent_as-plain-map-asia-robinson-267_geolocation.jpg\" id=\"imgME\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgME', '0%')\" class=\"imgcenter\"/>Figure 1: Map of the Middle East region. © Mapswire (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('dd4f3c8a-6624-4df5-93ac-37e0a4be9fdc'); return false;\"><i>Mapswire</i></a>).</p>",
